 3D Six-Pack is an affordable, easy-to-use plug-in that adds 250+ terrific
 3D transitions to Sony Vegas and Sony Vegas Movie Studio. It provides
 better-looking, more realistic/natural replacements to existing 3D transitions
 plus new additions long-requested by users.

 3D Six-Pack includes:

 Particles
 51 particle transitions - a terrific variety of luminance-based particle drops
 (an industry exclusive that ties into dark/light areas of your images),
 fountain-like particle pours, and realistic particle swirls and trails.
 Must be seen to be believed!

 BurstFX
 30 exciting particle transitions that realistically burst and explode your
 scene into pieces to reveal the next clip. Features amazingly realistic
 particle motion outward with acceleration and fading.

 DepthFX
 41 unique 3D distortions, 3D twists/spins, stretches, swings, and more. Subtle
 motion acceleration and transparency changes provide a more natural look than
 any similar 3D transitions in your system.

 EnergyFX
 30 "natural" transitions that use wind, gravity, or other organic progressions
 to reveal the next scene. These are especially handy when you desire an
 eye-catching transition that looks "real" and energetic.

 ExtraFX
 40 additional transitions that were too cool to leave out - page-turn
 transitions based on particle motion, additional particle fountains, random
 line transitions, and very cool accelerated slides/squeezes!

 PageFX
 60 beautiful page turns, page peels, rolls/twists, etc. for wedding videos,
 family videos, etc. Realistic reflections and depth, smoothly accelerated
 motion, and subtle transparency changes combine to provide superb high-end
 output.


 for Sony Vegas / Vegas Movie Studio
